Request Info
------------
   Created: <%= @r.created_at %>
   Changed: <%= @r.updated_at %>
   Request: #<%= @r.id %> 
      Type: <%= @r.type_name %>
     State: <%= @r.state %>
      User: <%= @r.user_id %> <%= @r.user_id && @r.user.login %>
     Admin: <%= @r.admin_id %> <%= @r.admin_id && @r.admin.login %>
  Response: <%= @r.admin_response %>
    API IP: <%= @r.api_ip_addr %>
   API PTR: <%= @r.api_ip_ptr %>
 Client IP: <%= @r.client_ip_addr %>
Client PTR: <%= @r.client_ip_ptr %>

Requested changes
-----------------
<% @r.each_change do |attr, new_v, cur_v| %>
<%= attr.to_s.gsub(/_/, ' ').capitalize %>
  From: <%= cur_v %>
  To:   <%= new_v %> 
<% end %>

Reason for change: <%= @r.change_reason %>

Take action
-----------

  - See details: <%= @webui_url %>/?page=adminm&action=request_details&id=<%= @r.id %>&type=<%= @r.type_name %>

  - Approve:     <%= @webui_url %>/?page=adminm&action=request_process&id=<%= @r.id %>&type=<%= @r.type_name %>&rule=approve

  - Deny:        <%= @webui_url %>/?page=adminm&action=request_process&id=<%= @r.id %>&type=<%= @r.type_name %>&rule=deny

  - Ignore:      <%= @webui_url %>/?page=adminm&action=request_process&id=<%= @r.id %>&type=<%= @r.type_name %>&rule=ignore
